public func pad_left(value: text, width: int, fill: text) -> text
```

Preenche a esquerda ate atingir a largura indicada.
---

--- @target: pad_right
```zt
public func pad_right(value: text, width: int, fill: text) -> text
```

Preenche a direita ate atingir a largura indicada.
---

--- @target: replace_all
```zt
public func replace_all(value: text, needle: text, replacement: text) -> text
```

Troca todas as ocorrencias de `needle` por `replacement`.
---

--- @target: replace
```zt
public func replace(value: text, needle: text, replacement: text) -> text
```

Alias de compatibilidade para `replace_all`.
